detailedDescription.articleBody: Pride and Prejudice is a romantic novel of manners written by Jane Austen in 1813. detailedDescription.articleBody: The University of Pennsylvania is a private Ivy League research university in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. The university claims a founding date of 1740 and is one of the nine colonial colleges chartered prior to the U.S. Declaration of Independence.
